'''胸膜炎'''（Pleurisy）是指圍繞於[[肺部|肺部]]及[[胸腔|胸腔]]內側的黏膜（[[胸膜|胸膜]]）[[發炎|發炎]]<ref name=NIH2011WHAT/>。這會導致呼吸時急劇的[[胸痛|胸痛]]<ref name=NIH2011WHAT>{{cite web|title=What Are Pleurisy and Other Pleural Disorders?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/pleurisy|website=NHLBI|accessdate=1 November 2016|date=21 September 2011|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161108065923/https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/pleurisy|archivedate=8 November 2016}}</ref>。其他症狀取決於潛在的病因，可能包括[[呼吸短促|呼吸短促]]、[[咳嗽|咳嗽]]、[[發燒|發燒]]或[[體重減輕|體重減輕]]<ref name=NIH2011SYM>{{cite web|title=What Are the Signs and Symptoms of Pleurisy and Other Pleural Disorders|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/pleurisy/signs|website=NHLBI|accessdate=1 November 2016|date=21 September 2011|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008061144/https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/pleurisy/signs|archivedate=8 October 2016}}</ref>。有時疼痛可能是持續的鈍痛<ref name=NIH2011SYM/>。

最常見的原因是[[病毒感染|病毒感染]]<ref name=NIH2011CA/>。其他原因包括[[肺炎|肺炎]]、[[肺栓塞|肺栓塞]]、[[自體免疫性疾病|自體免疫性疾病]]、[[肺癌|肺癌]]、心臟手術後、[[胰臟炎|胰臟炎]]、胸部創傷和[[石棉沉著症|石棉沉著症]]<ref name=NIH2011CA/>，有時原因仍然是未知的<ref name=NIH2011CA>{{cite web|title=What Causes Pleurisy and Other Pleural Disorders?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/pleurisy/causes|website=NHLBI|accessdate=1 November 2016|date=21 September 2011|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008061131/https://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/pleurisy/causes|archivedate=8 October 2016}}</ref>。主要的機轉是胸膜互相摩擦而非平順的滑動<ref name=NIH2011WHAT/>。其他可能產生類似症狀的病症包括[[心包炎|心包炎]]、[[心肌梗塞|心肌梗塞]]、[[膽囊炎|膽囊炎]]和[[氣胸|氣胸]]<ref name=FER2016/>。診斷包括[[胸部X光|胸部X光]]檢查，[[心電圖|心電圖]]（ECG）和[[血液檢查|血液檢查]]<ref name=FER2016>{{cite book|last1=Ferri|first1=Fred F.|title=Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2017: 5 Books in 1|date=2016|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=9780323448383|page=981|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=rRhCDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA981|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103215630/https://books.google.ca/books?id=rRhCDAAAQBAJ&pg=PA981|archivedate=3 November 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Kass|first1=SM|last2=Williams|first2=PM|last3=Reamy|first3=BV|title=Pleurisy.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_american-family-physician_2007-05-01_75_9/page/1357|journal=American Family Physician|date=1 May 2007|volume=75|issue=9|pages=1357–64|pmid=17508531}}</ref>。

治療取決於根本原因<ref name=FER2016/>。[[乙醯氨酚|乙醯氨酚]]和[[布洛芬|布洛芬]]可用於幫助緩解疼痛<ref name=NIH2011TX>{{cite web|title=How Are Pleurisy and Other Pleural Disorders Treated?|url=http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/pleurisy/treatment|website=NHLBI|accessdate=1 November 2016|date=21 September 2011|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103233948/http://www.nhlbi.nih.gov/health/health-topics/topics/pleurisy/treatment|archivedate=3 November 2016}}</ref>。建議可以使用[[誘發性肺量計|誘發性肺量計]]來促進呼吸。在[[美國|美國]]每年大約有一百萬人受到影響<ref name=DI2012>{{cite book|title=Disease & Drug Consult: Respiratory Disorders|date=2012|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=9781451151947|page=Pleurisy|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=bdkPAAAAQBAJ&pg=PT175|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103215903/https://books.google.ca/books?id=bdkPAAAAQBAJ&pg=PT175|archivedate=3 November 2016}}</ref>。[[希波克拉底|希波克拉底]]早在公元前400年就已經描述過此病症<ref>{{cite book|last1=Light|first1=Richard W.|last2=Lee|first2=Y. C. Gary|title=Textbook of Pleural Diseases Second Edition|date=2008|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=9780340940174|page=2|edition=2|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=v5T0MWmBLDYC&pg=PA2|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161103215905/https://books.google.ca/books?id=v5T0MWmBLDYC&pg=PA2|archivedate=3 November 2016}}</ref>。

